Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.43,0:00:06.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy! You can hear me, can't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:10.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! I swear I'll get you outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.02,0:00:20.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warning. Another one of the \Nengraved seals has been removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:25.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If the remaining three disappear, the \Nowners will lose the right of possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:27.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy! Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:33.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Struggle how you might, it's pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:37.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In mere moments, Lucy Heartfilia \Nwill merge with the Infinity Clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:43.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And when that happens, it'll become possible \Nfor us to take control of Real Nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:44.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:47.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone lay a hand on Nee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's going to stay with me forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:51.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.81,0:00:53.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For eternity...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently on Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:32.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While we were fighting with Legion \Nover the memento from Lucy's dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:36.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,the new Oracion Seis appeared before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.39,0:02:39.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They stole the Infinity \NClock and abducted Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:44.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We handpicked members headed for Infinity \NCastle to try to stop Real Nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:48.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can defeat all Six Generals barring \Nour way, we'll be able to stop Real Nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:50.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, there are three left!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:02:58.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday, Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:02.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mama, Papa, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:04.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:07.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:13.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. She said \Nthat was all a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu! What's going on over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:18.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Lucy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:20.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:23.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy's gonna be swallowed \Nup by the Infinity Clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.78,0:03:24.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:29.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I Can Hear the Voices of My Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:34.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy is merging with the Infinity Clock?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:36.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That must be why we can't \Nreach her by telepathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:39.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to rest a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:43.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:45.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and beat Oracion Seis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:50.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If Lucy becomes one with the \NInfinity Clock, it'll be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:55.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.61,0:03:58.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to take me down \Nwithout a moment to spare,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:01.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,so my engraved seal on the \NInfinity Clock will be erased...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up, Titania!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:07.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,"Give up." I don't know \Nwhat those words mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:11.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're defeated, \Nyou still have friends, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:14.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can rely on them, but you won't beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.99,0:04:15.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:22.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to receive our new powers, \Nwe each lost something irreplaceable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.22,0:04:24.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For Erigor, it was his memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:26.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For Racer, it was his heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:28.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Angel, her lifespan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:32.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What you scum lack is the resolve \Nto lose something important!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:35.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can surpass the \Nweight upon our hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:38.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:42.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Romeo! What are you doing over there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.02,0:04:46.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I stowed away on Christina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:49.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like this, there was \Nno way I was gonna stay home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.46,0:04:53.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! I know how you feel, but this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:54.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Romeo-san, can you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:55.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.01,0:04:58.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, meet up with somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:00.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, there's no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:03.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They have to beat the remaining \NOracion Seis members and save Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:05.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which way should I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.84,0:05:09.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you the route Natsu and \Nthe others took, so head that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.52,0:05:09.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:12.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy! Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:13.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?! I can hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.08,0:05:15.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're headin' that way, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.74,0:05:16.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:18.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, stop Samuel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:20.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:20.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:21.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the archbishop's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.29,0:05:24.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Byro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.29,0:05:27.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where's Gildarts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:31.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He descended into the \Ndepths with his comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.84,0:05:33.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect he's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:37.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, do you know what \Nhappened to Samuel and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:40.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no more reason to go after Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:43.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we defeat all Six Generals, \Ntheir seals will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:44.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And if that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.80,0:05:50.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're too late to stop Lucy Heartfilia \Nfrom merging with the Infinity Clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:52.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:54.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:56.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is still a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:05:59.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:02.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a... trying nightmare \Nfor the longest time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.51,0:06:07.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It had nothing to do with my own \Nwill. I was controlled like a puppet,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:10.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,which brought this situation on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:16.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However, taking no heed of the \Ndanger, these people rescued me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.29,0:06:21.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But even though I was manipulated, \NI saw from the enemy's viewpoint,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:23.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and amid this chaos...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:25.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.00,0:06:27.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something we'd like you to tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:31.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Archbishop, you know a lot about \Nthe Infinity Clock, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:36.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to know about the captured \NCelestial Spirit Wizard, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.86,0:06:40.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You say you wanna be with Lucy forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.36,0:06:43.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Lucy's feelings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.89,0:06:47.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She trusted you, and even after \Nshe realized you betrayed her,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,she wants to believe in you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:52.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you hear that voice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:55.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to hesitate over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:07:00.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just trying to take back \Nwhat you lost... Imitatia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:03.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:07.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Nee-san will be happier this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:11.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we were always together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:14.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.37,0:07:15.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Romeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:18.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you still lying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:21.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the real Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:24.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you were always \Ntogether, it was a big lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.83,0:07:26.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true! I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:33.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After Lucy-nee lost her family, imagine \Nhow happy she was when she met you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:37.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you betray her?! Why did \Nyou tell such an awful lie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She believed that you were her friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:45.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too... I thought you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:48.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddamn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:50.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Romeo-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:54.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't let them shake you, Imitatia-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.93,0:07:58.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who stands in your way is an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:02.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something... Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:03.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Romeo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.69,0:08:15.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:20.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it, Michelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:24.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Figuring out who the hell \Nyou are can wait 'til later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.94,0:08:28.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I'm gonna kick \Nyour ass an' save Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:30.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:35.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! This should be an amusing spectacle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:36.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shy away, Imitatia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:40.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the new Oracion Seis's number two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.81,0:08:43.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make your prayers come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:44.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But first, show me your allegiance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:55.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:57.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wench...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:00.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:09.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All you need think about is your most fervent wish, \Nliving together with Lucy Heartfilia for eternity...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.32,0:09:11.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:16.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do whatever is needed to \Nmake your prayer come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.03,0:09:21.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bind that man, my vines!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.43,0:09:27.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:32.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warning. Murderous intent detected \Nnearby, approaching rapidly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:34.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Murderous intent?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:40.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Samuel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:42.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.67,0:09:44.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy Heartfilia!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:48.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stop the Infinity Clock \Nby spilling your blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.33,0:10:15.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Coco, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.25,0:10:17.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:19.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to argue with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:24.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tear through me with those claws first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.67,0:10:29.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You... I'm not doing this for \Nthe sake of church doctrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:31.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm following my own heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:33.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you know it's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:34.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:40.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But to put an end to this \Nchaos, I have no other choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:43.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.40,0:10:46.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.55,0:10:47.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the answer you arrived at?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:56.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna wipe that decision to \Ntake a life right out of your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:10:57.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:10:57.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:00.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sammy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:02.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:05.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Can you hear me?! Lucy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:08.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I... can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.66,0:11:15.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is lying on the \Nground in front of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:19.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:22.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:25.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:28.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.05,0:11:31.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She can hear our voices!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:34.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy's fightin', too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:38.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This showdown ain't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:44.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, he's stubborn! This is why I \Nsaid he should be taken out for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:47.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph. Whatever he tries to do, it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You people have no chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:53.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:57.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want power that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:12:03.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is spreading chaos and destruction and \Ngetting revenge that important to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:05.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:10.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't accomplish this, I won't \Nbe able to look Cubelious in the face!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:16.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing else left to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.47,0:12:20.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I threw away everything, \Nso I'm afraid of nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.06,0:12:24.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing you can do, Titania!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:32.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, listen! There's a way to slow down \Nthe merging of Lucy and the Infinity Clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:35.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The archbishop will explain, \Nso listen carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:36.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His Grace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:41.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,To merge with a sacrificial Celestial Spirit Wizard,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.00,0:12:47.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it takes a telepathic bond to be \Nformed with the person and her sense of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:50.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it must \Nintegrate with her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:59.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For that, the chains descending from the \NInfinity Castle to the ground spread Real Nightmare,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:03.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,while at the same time taking in the \Nland's magic power and all memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:09.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Put another way, you can buy \Nsome time by cutting the chains!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:11.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Byro and Zentopia's monk \Nsoldiers already left!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:14.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, destroy the chains!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:19.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They look like they'll be filling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:23.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I heard it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.77,0:13:26.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nii-san. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:29.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. Everybody makes mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.28,0:13:31.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:33.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's important...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:37.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...is what you do afterwards, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:39.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's snap those chains, Sammy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.24,0:13:44.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's have a contest to see who \Ncan chop through the most, Nii-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:47.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Talons of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.41,0:13:51.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What tenacity! This is the \Npower of your feelings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:56.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I still had a chance, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:13:57.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A faint hope at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:00.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, do your worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:03.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to dispose of you in one stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:10.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cubelious... I'm going to use...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.92,0:14:12.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...the last breath you gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the second generation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:18.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Decay and die, Titania!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:22.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Poison Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:26.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.38,0:14:33.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This ancient weapon is \Nsaid to keep evil at bay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:36.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I can use it like this, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.76,0:14:40.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you can't ask about \Nwhat you don't know, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.51,0:14:43.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you'd pull \Nthat out at the eleventh hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:45.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Try listening to my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:49.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:53.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sever the chains... You intend \Nto bring us both down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.11,0:14:56.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting with one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:06.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:11.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.98,0:15:16.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh, that tastes like shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:19.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in high spirits, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.47,0:15:22.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let her outdo me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:30.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're heading to the next chain! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:38.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the archbishop's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:41.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't have to do anything \Nwith a guild or Legion!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:45.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just doing this to correct my mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.56,0:15:47.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my fifth one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:49.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I did seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:56.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Calling me... He's calling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:15:58.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting closer and closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.01,0:16:01.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:03.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:04.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cobra...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:08.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you're strong because \Nyou lost everything, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:11.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not true strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:14.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:18.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,People get stronger when they've \Ngot something to protect!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:22.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got a real \Nfriend, they support you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:28.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you only think about yourself! Could \Nyou really hear the voice of your friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:34.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't feel shame now when you \Nthink of your friend or whatever?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:38.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:41.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you went too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:45.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's as far as you get. \NI'm gonna crush your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:53.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cubelious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.50,0:16:59.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... But... I sense her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.19,0:17:03.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her form has changed... but \NI can hear her thoughts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:07.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't have been a \Nmistake! There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.77,0:17:11.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to lose your \Ncomposure in the heat of battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.22,0:17:13.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:23.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings for friends don't drag you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:26.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You actually realize it, too, don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:28.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Cobra?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:35.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You can hear \Nthe voice of your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:38.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you throw everything away that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.13,0:17:42.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:45.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard his voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:48.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A shooting star...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:51.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! It must be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:54.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's come to get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.03,0:17:59.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warning. Another engraved \Nseal has been erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:01.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:04.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cobra-sama is down?! I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:03.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.30,0:18:09.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Now I just gotta \Nmop the floor with you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:11.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a tenacious man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:14.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're only buying time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:16.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not having any \Neffect on the big picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:22.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What my father left undone... The \Ndestruction of everything that has form...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.74,0:18:25.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And bringing about nothingness and chaos...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:27.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It didn't work seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:31.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But this time, I won't let you \Ninterfere, Natsu Dragneel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.47,0:18:34.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:38.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.50,0:18:43.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Infinity Clock girl that \Nyou're trying to save...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:45.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already too late to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:50.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,100 years of sleep is as \Nsimple as falling off a log.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:54.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy Heartfilia is becoming \Npart of the Infinity Clock,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.19,0:18:57.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and when it's done, she'll \Nlose her body and mind, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:02.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And once she's become a piece of the clock, \Nshe'll be erased from everyone's memories as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:06.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her very existence will be wiped \Noff the face of Earthland.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:13.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erased... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:16.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Nee-san is going \Nto be together with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:18.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just going to become a tool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:24.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can be with her as much as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:31.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll work out well. For someone like \Nyou, she'll be the perfect partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.26,0:19:33.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:36.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:40.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What I wished for...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:43.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What I prayed for...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:45.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:48.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:52.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:53.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.41,0:19:55.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:59.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.15,0:20:04.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:07.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:10.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:13.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cry a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.21,0:20:15.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.78,0:20:17.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of clumsy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:22.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:29.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't prick your conscience, anyone \Ncould easily make those choices, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:34.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Michelle was also suffering...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.77,0:20:44.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, no. This is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.63,0:20:45.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:49.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Imitatia, your role is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.78,0:20:50.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:57.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.18,0:21:17.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:20.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.74,0:21:22.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:28.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:32.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not that. That's not it. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:35.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to... the way it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.34,0:21:36.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:44.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere along the line, I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:52.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl was my precious little sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.34,0:21:58.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic, filthy doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.92,0:22:03.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, stop that... You'll get \Nyour shoe dirty! Good one, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.45,0:22:04.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.61,0:22:07.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu-nii!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:13.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:18.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it that funny to you when someone's sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.60,0:22:23.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll beat you 'til you \Nwon't even be able to crack a smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.14,0:23:58.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh! At this rate, Lucy's gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:24:00.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just one left! Brain II!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.09,0:24:06.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But it feels like his hatred is \Nstronger than anyone else's in Oracion Seis.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.67,0:24:07.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, we're not gonna lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.18,0:24:13.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're carrying the combined will of everyone \Nin Fairy Tail on our shoulders as we fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.15,0:24:16.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Lucy and Michelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.07,0:24:17.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.23,0:24:19.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'm the one that's fightin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.07,0:24:21.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to bring that up now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.81,0:24:24.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna let you get \Naway with just soundin' cool!
